child on the right, and the rightmost child has no child to the right to compare against.&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>Leetcode Algorithms 14</title><link>https://kes.github.io/leetcode/leetcode-algorithms-14/</link><pubDate>Thu, 28 Nov 2024 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://kes.github.io/leetcode/leetcode-algorithms-14/</guid><description>&lt;p&gt;Okay, this is the fourteenth question from the &amp;ldquo;Top Interview 150.&amp;rdquo;&lt;/p&gt;
